## Phase 6 — Agent 6 (Document Vault)

### 6.1 Agent 6: Vault — `src/agents/vault.js`

**Functions:**

| Function | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `processDocument(file, source, emailContext, userId)` | Full pipeline: analyze → dedup → compress → store → index |
| `analyzeDocument(file)` | Gemini Vision API call → returns doc_type, vendor, amount, tags |
| `isDuplicate(userId, fileBuffer)` | MD5 hash check against `vault_metadata.file_hash` |
| `compressFile(file)` | `sharp` for images (max 100KB), text extraction for docs |
| `storeFile(userId, file)` | Upload to Supabase Storage bucket `vault` |
| `indexDocument(userId, metadata)` | INSERT into `vault_metadata` with all extracted fields |
| `findDocument(userId, naturalQuery)` | Gemini extracts search intent → query `vault_metadata` |
| `getDocument(userId, docId)` | Fetch file from Supabase Storage |
| `shareDocument(userId, docId, recipientEmail)` | Download from vault → send as email attachment |
| `calculateExpiry(importance)` | `permanent`→null, `90days`→+90d, `30days`→+30d |
| `checkExpiries(userId)` | Daily 8am — find docs expiring in 3 days → notify |

**Supabase Storage config:**
- Bucket: `vault` (private)
- Path format: `{userId}/{uuid}_{originalFilename}`
- Max file: 50MB (Supabase free tier limit)

