## Phase 8 — Agent 10 (Mentor)

### 8.1 Agent 10: Mentor — `src/agents/mentor.js`

**Functions:**

| Function | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `runScheduledJob(jobName, userId)` | Dispatcher for all scheduled tasks |
| `sendMorningDigest(userId)` | 7am — overnight summary + pending items |
| `checkSystemHealth(userId)` | 8am — API usage, DB size, vault size, uptime |
| `checkDocumentExpiries(userId)` | 8am — docs expiring in 3 days |
| `sendEveningPromoDigest(userId)` | 6pm — curated promos with value scoring |
| `sendWeeklyReport(userId)` | Mon 9am — stats, suggestions, awaiting replies |
| `scanSpamFolder(userId)` | Every 30 min — rescue valuable emails from spam |
| `checkFollowUps(userId)` | Every 60 min — sent emails with no reply > X days |
| `detectToneDrift(userId)` | Weekly — compare writing style evolution |
| `calculateRescueScore(email, memory)` | Spam scoring: known domain +60, replied-to +70, VIP +80, high-value content +35 |
| `scorePromoValue(email, memory)` | Promo scoring: purchased-from +40, 30%+ discount +30, expiring +25 |
| `detectSenderPatterns(userId)` | Find senders who email on consistent days → suggest templates |

**Scheduled intervals (set in `server.js` startup):**

```javascript
// Timezone-aware scheduling using setTimeout chains
scheduleDaily('07:00', () => mentor.sendMorningDigest(userId))
scheduleDaily('08:00', () => mentor.checkSystemHealth(userId))
scheduleDaily('08:00', () => mentor.checkDocumentExpiries(userId))
scheduleDaily('18:00', () => mentor.sendEveningPromoDigest(userId))
scheduleWeekly('Monday', '09:00', () => mentor.sendWeeklyReport(userId))
setInterval(() => mentor.scanSpamFolder(userId), 30 * 60 * 1000)
setInterval(() => mentor.checkFollowUps(userId), 60 * 60 * 1000)
setInterval(() => autonomy.checkPendingSends(), 60 * 1000)
```

---

## Phase 9 — Telegram Command System

### 9.1 Command Router — `src/routes/telegram.js`

`POST /webhook/telegram` → parses update → routes to handler.

### 9.2 Full Command List — 24 Commands

**Inbox commands:**
| Command | Handler function | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `/inbox` | `handleInbox(userId)` | Today's important emails |
| `/pending` | `handlePending(userId)` | Emails waiting for user reply |
| `/sent` | `handleSent(userId)` | What PA sent today |
| `/search [text]` | `handleSearch(userId, query)` | Natural language email search |

**Vault commands:**
| Command | Handler |
|---|---|
| `/vault` | `handleVaultList(userId)` — recent docs |
| `/find [desc]` | `handleVaultFind(userId, query)` — NL doc search |
| `/files` | `handleFilesList(userId)` — uploaded files |
| `/share [name] to [email]` | `handleShare(userId, name, email)` |

**Contact commands:**
| Command | Handler |
|---|---|
| `/vip add/remove/list [email]` | `handleVIP(userId, action, email)` |
| `/ignore add/list [email\|domain]` | `handleIgnore(userId, action, target)` |
| `/neveragain` | `handleNeverAgain(userId, replyToEmail)` |

**Status commands:**
| Command | Handler |
|---|---|
| `/away [duration]` | `handleAway(userId, duration)` |
| `/back` | `handleBack(userId)` |
| `/pause` / `/resume` | `handlePauseResume(userId, action)` |
| `/status` | `handleStatus(userId)` |

**Settings commands:**
| Command | Handler |
|---|---|
| `/tone [formal\|casual\|friendly]` | `handleTone(userId, style)` |
| `/autonomy [high\|low]` | `handleAutonomy(userId, level)` |
| `/undo` | `handleUndo(userId)` |
| `/undo window [mins]` | `handleUndoWindow(userId, mins)` |
| `/whitelist add/remove/list [category]` | `handleWhitelist(userId, action, cat)` |
| `/help` | `handleHelp(userId)` — full command reference |

**Natural language handler:**
Any non-command text → `handleNaturalLanguage(userId, text)` → Gemini classifies intent → routes to vault_search / email_search / draft_request / status_query / command.

**Callback query handler:**
Button presses (Send, Edit, Reject, Undo, Later, etc.) → `handleCallback(callbackQuery)` → routes to appropriate agent.

