## Build Order & Dependencies

```mermaid
graph TD
    P1["Phase 1: Foundation + DB"] --> P2["Phase 2: Intake + Filter"]
    P1 --> P3["Phase 3: Context + AI Brain"]
    P2 --> P3
    P3 --> P4["Phase 4: Autonomy + Notification"]
    P4 --> P5["Phase 5: Send Agent"]
    P1 --> P6["Phase 6: Document Vault"]
    P1 --> P7["Phase 7: Memory Agent"]
    P5 --> P8["Phase 8: Mentor Agent"]
    P4 --> P9["Phase 9: Telegram Commands"]
    P8 --> P10["Phase 10: Health + Deploy"]
    P9 --> P10
```

**Critical path:** Phase 1 → 2 → 3 → 4 → 5 (core email flow working end-to-end)
**Parallel work:** Phase 6 (Vault) and Phase 7 (Memory) can start after Phase 1
